      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BLOW TORCH (1) drew a squeeze box and was game in defeat when a close third, 0.8 lengths from the winner Inga Amy (22.73) at Warrnambool. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings four times from seven starts. Top chance in this line up. DRAGON BLACK (8) has mixed form a little and missed the frame the last two but was a Grade 5 winner three back (22.96) at this track over 400m. Can feature with the right run. MUSTANG ELEANOR (2) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing fourth (23.15) in a Grade 5 at Ballarat. Will give the top chances plenty to think about. BONDED (3) picked up an unexpected cheque last time and is in the mix again.",
